  body " gré]] à\n|fy=[[tankje]]\n|fur=[[ringraciâ]], [[ingraciâ]], [[graciâ]]\n|kjh=\n|ha=\n|hi=[[धन्यवाद देना]] (dhanyavād denā), [[शुक्रिया करना]] (shukriyā karnā)\n|hr=[[zahvaljivati]]\n|rom=\n|ce=\n|c"
